tc_game_scripts.description: Updates your server to the selected beta version
tc_game_scripts.script_contents:
from System.Diagnostics import Process
version = str(ThisService.Variables['betaversion']) ipport = str(ThisService.IpAddress) + str(ThisService.GamePort)
p = Process() p.StartInfo.RedirectStandardOutput = True p.StartInfo.RedirectStandardError = True p.StartInfo.UseShellExecute = False p.StartInfo.CreateNoWindow = True p.StartInfo.FileName = TCAdminFolder+'\\Monitor\\Tools\\SteamCmd\\steamcmd.exe' p.StartInfo.Arguments = '+login anonymous +force_install_dir ' + ThisService.RootDirectory + ' +app_update 740 -beta ' + version + ' validate +quit' p.StartInfo.WorkingDirectory=ThisService.WorkingDirectory p.Start() Script.WriteToConsole('Installing version ' + version + ' on ' + ipport + '...') while not p.StandardOutput.EndOfStream: Script.WriteToConsole(str(p.StandardOutput.ReadLine())) p.WaitForExit()
